 Come RENT Your New Dream Home with SOLAR! This magnificent 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence spans an impressive 3,043 square feet, offering ample space and luxurious features throughout. New Paint Upstairs. Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this property is perfect for those seeking both comfort and elegance. The heart of this residence is undoubtedly the chef's kitchen, a culinary masterpiece that will delight even the most discerning home cook. The kitchen showcases a spacious breakfast bar and a convenient kitchen island, providing ample space for entertaining guests or enjoying casual family meals. Adorned with elegant granite countertops, this kitchen offers a perfect blend of style and functionality. Close to 303, I-10, Shopping, Luke AFB!!

Seller will pay for the pool maintenance.
